{
  "stem": "3100.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all put in in five in abreast or six in abreast and marched to the Bahnhof station, which was the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as they marched with them, by the time they marched with them, already [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] day-- night fall took place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took them, and we didn't know happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all we heard is shooting, and yelling, and screaming, and crying from the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I went back to my home, and I was staying in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I looked around, and I don't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was alone left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I heard that some of the Judenrat members came and said, whoever could go out, please help us to gather.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's a lot of dead people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let us gather them and bring them to a burial place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, I went out that night with a few others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We gathered all the dead people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if I recall, there must have been 80, 85 people-- women, children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we brought-- we took them a place called the morgue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went and looked at everyone's face, and I couldn't recognize anybody that should be from my family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I lifted up my eyes to God and I thanked him that at least I didn't see anybody dead of my family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Little did I know at that time, that would have been a blessing if I could get somebody from the my-- from my family that I could at least bring them to a Jewish burial and the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, to find out later what happened is they took them in to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to train, to wagons, or to car cattle's.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just put them in there. 100, 150 in a car cattle, as many as they could.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
